           email = "evanmascitti@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Special functions for manipulating 3D meshes and deriving metrics from their geometry. Written for author's PhD project on engineered infield soils for baseball and softball fields.
